-- Berlusconi Probed by Rome Prosecutor for Alleged Tax Evasion, Ansa Reports
-- B y   J e f f r e y   D o n o v a n
-- 2010-10-15T09:31:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/berlusconi-probed-by-rome-prosecutor-for-alleged-tax-evasion-ansa-reports.html
Italian Prime Minister Silvio
Berlusconi has come under investigation by Rome prosecutors for
alleged tax evasion at his Mediaset SpA company, Ansa news
agency reported today, without saying where it got the
information.  The probe is related to an ongoing investigation in Milan
of the purchase of film and televison rights by Mediaset, Ansa
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jeffrey Donovan at 
 jdonovan26@bloomberg.net  